            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3ETroubles%20come%20in%20many%20forms%2C%20shapes%2C%20and%20sizes%20and%20include%20anything%20that%20disturbs%20the%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20of%20your%20life.%20Two%20things%20must%20be%20expected%20when%20you%20follow%20the%20Lord%3A%20First%2C%20the%20devil%20will%20throw%20his%20fiery%20darts%20to%20try%20to%20discourage%20you%20through%20troubling%20circumstances.%20Second%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20affliction%2C%20the%20Lord%20will%20deliver%20you.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHow%20does%20He%20do%20it%3F%20The%20Word%20of%20God%20says%2C%20%22The%20eyes%20of%20the%20Lord%20watch%20over%20those%20who%20do%20right%3B%20his%20ears%20are%20open%20to%20their%20cries%20for%20help%22%20(Psalm%2034%3A15).%20Furthermore%2C%20%22The%20Lord%20hears%20his%20people%20when%20they%20call%20to%20him%20for%20help.%20He%20rescues%20them%20from%20all%20their%20troubles%22%20(v.%2017).%20%20The%20Lord%20is%20watching%20you%20and%20listening%20to%20you%20when%20you%20walk%20through%20difficulties%2C%20and%20He%20is%20eager%20to%20rescue%20you%20from%20any%20trouble.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20disciples%20faced%20the%20deepest%20despair%20and%20trouble%20of%20their%20lives%20after%20the%20crucifixion%20of%20Christ.%20Little%20did%20they%20know%2C%20however%2C%20that%20God%20had%20a%20plan%20and%20was%20going%20to%20resurrect%20Christ!%20That's%20the%20way%20it%20is%20for%20us%2C%20too.%20We%20don't%20always%20realize%20that%20God%20is%20in%20control%20in%20every%20circumstance%20of%20life%20and%20has%20a%20plan%20of%20resurrection%20waiting%20to%20unfold.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhen%20you%20see%20the%20%22trouble%22%20side%20in%20life%2C%20hang%20in%20there.%20You%20will%20surely%20see%20the%20%22delivering%22%20side%20as%20well!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
